{"id":51848,"title":"[A healthcare network reintroducing diabetic people to physical activity].","abstract":"The Paris Diabetes Network helps diabetic people to live more easily with their disease. Surrounded by professionals, the patients benefit from an innovative care approach which places as much emphasis on physical activity as on diet and treatments. In addition to the medical benefits, pleasure and fun are very much on the agenda.","date":"2014-03-24","categories":"Endocrine System Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24654329","annotations":[{"name":"Medicine","weight":0.801843,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medicine"},{"name":"Health care","weight":0.784197,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health_care"},{"name":"Physical exercise","weight":0.762559,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Physical_exercise"},{"name":"Disease","weight":0.705743,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disease"},{"name":"Diet (nutrition)","weight":0.510032,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diet_(nutrition)"},{"name":"Diabetes mellitus","weight":0.480865,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diabetes_mellitus"},{"name":"Paris","weight":0.268509,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paris"},{"name":"Pleasure","weight":0.0532834,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pleasure"},{"name":"Physics","weight":0.0250212,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Physics"},{"name":"Computer network","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Computer_network"}]}
